Prerequisites :

You need a recent version of SDL (I use SDL-1.1.5). 
The 1.0 serie don't work, sorry.

Installation :

Just do make, it should work (I hope :)
If you dont want opengl mode comment the line
GL_MODE = 1 in the Makefile

Use :

gngb [option] game 
option:
-h            : show this help
-a            : auto frame skip
-g            : force normal gameboy
-f            : fullscreen
-j joy_num    : use joy_num as joystick 
-s            : sound on
-r            : rumble on
-o            : opengl renderer
-O WxH        : same as o, but with WxH resolution (instead of double size)


Key :

Enter          : Start
Right Shift    : Select
W              : B       (on azerty kerboard)
X              : A    

F9             : fullscreen on/off
Shift + F(1-8) : save state (experimental)
F(1-8)         : load state (experimental)

